# Multilingual Translation Concepts

## Core Concepts
- **Languages**: Defined in [Includes/Models/Languages.php](mdc:Includes/Models/Languages.php)
- **Posts**: Translatable content in [Includes/Models/Translatable/](mdc:Includes/Models/Translatable/)
- **Terms**: Translatable taxonomies in [Includes/Models/Translatable/](mdc:Includes/Models/Translatable/)
- **Strings**: User-defined translatable strings

## Language Management
- Language objects created via [Includes/Factories/language-factory.php](mdc:Includes/Factories/language-factory.php)
- Language settings in [Settings/Controllers/languages.php](mdc:Settings/Controllers/languages.php)
- Language flags stored in [flags/](mdc:flags/) directory

## Translation Process
1. **Content Creation**: Posts/terms created in default language
2. **Translation Linking**: Content linked across languages
3. **Translation**: Manual or AI-powered translation
4. **Synchronization**: Content sync across languages

## URL Structure
- **Domain-based**: Different domains per language
- **Directory-based**: `/lang/` subdirectories
- **URL-based**: Language codes in URLs
- Handled by [Includes/Services/Links/](mdc:Includes/Services/Links/)

## Content Types
- **Posts**: Blog posts, pages, custom post types
- **Terms**: Categories, tags, custom taxonomies
- **Strings**: User-defined translatable text
- **Options**: WordPress options (blog name, description)

## Machine Translation
- AI-powered translation in [modules/machine-translation/](mdc:modules/machine-translation/)
- Integration with external translation services
- Preview functionality for translations

## Synchronization
- Content sync across languages in [modules/sync/](mdc:modules/sync/)
- Meta field synchronization
- Content relationships maintained

## Frontend Features
- Language switcher widgets
- URL translation
- Content filtering by language
- SEO-friendly URLs

## Admin Interface
- Translation management in [Admin/Controllers/](mdc:Admin/Controllers/)
- Bulk translation operations
- Translation status indicators
- Content relationship management
